text:
I just wanna shout out that the customer service from @ImportImageRace is top notch! Since @UPS has massively failed to get a parcel across the country, IIR has stepped up and is taking the initiative to get things going correctly!

Thanks Import Image Racing!

#ImportImageRacing

@UPS why is it so hard to move a parcel from the east coast to the west coast when the customer picks 3 Day Select?

Day 1 - That's a nice parcel.
Day 2 - Damn! What's that doiing here? Put it on a plane!
Day 3 - Pick up from airport, sort, and deliver.

Is that so difficult?
@TheSelfEmployed @UPS Here's a tip: Don't pick UPS. Brown will fail you, and not even know what's wrong.

@Smithcraft1 I can understand waiting for a package is not fun. I would be happy to check the status of your package. Please DM your tracking number, delivery address, and phone number. ^BO https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ

@Smithcraft1 Our team can review your tracking history to see if we can identify the delay. For assistance, DM us the tracking number, name, and complete address on the package. ^TT https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ

@UPSHelp I already talked to a CSR .

Why would it matter after UPS failed?

@UPSHelp It gets even better! Instead of sending it to the local airport, they sent it to the airport 150 miles away! That's a good way to add an extra day!

Way to go!
@Smithcraft1 If you would like further assistance, please DM the tracking number and delivery address to the link provided. ^SB https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
@UPSHelp There's no way to get the parcel here on time, so what assistance would you be able to provide?
